  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Class 3 Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Chemical Manufacturing MNC. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Class 3 Driver to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the East.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description: </strong></p><ul><li>Load, transport, and deliver items safely and within designated timeframes.</li><li>Conduct pickups and deliveries for assigned areas as per company requirements</li><li>Prioritize and ensure timely delivery of urgent or high-priority goods</li><li>Verify orders before and after delivery to confirm accuracy and customer satisfaction.</li><li>Maintain the vehicle in proper working condition and report any issues promptly.</li><li>Follow assigned routes and adhere to scheduled delivery times.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisors</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possesses <strong>Class 3 Driving License</strong></li><li>At Least 1 year of driving experience</li><li>Able to handle loading/unloading of goods</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: </strong><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></a></p><p>EA License No: 19C9682<br />EA Personnel No: R2198636<br />EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</p>",
